#: ../../source/docs/user_manual/introduction/general_tools.rst:231
msgid "**Quickly share a layer style**"
msgstr ""

#: ../../source/docs/user_manual/introduction/general_tools.rst:233
msgid ""
"From the context menu, copy the style of a layer and paste it to a group "
"or a selection of layers: the style is applied to all the layers that are"
" of the same type (vector vs raster) as the original layer and, in case "
"of vector, have the same geometry type (point, line or polygon)."
