#: ../../source/docs/user_manual/introduction/general_tools.rst:244
msgid "Working with the Legend independent layer order"
msgstr ""

#: ../../source/docs/user_manual/introduction/general_tools.rst:246
msgid ""
"There is a panel that allows you to define an independent drawing order "
"for the layers panel. You can activate it in the menu "
":menuselection:`Settings --> Panels --> Layer Order Panel`. This feature "
"allows you to, for instance, order your layers in order of importance, "
"but still display them in the correct order (see figure_layer_order_; you"
" can notice that the ``airports`` features are displayed over the "
"``alaska`` polygon despite their layers placement in the Layers panel). "
"Unchecking the |checkbox| :guilabel:`Control rendering order` box "
"underneath the list of layers will cause a revert to default behavior."
msgstr ""

